Yes. All - all - practically everybody in the primary school were - from round about the neighbourhood and all in about the same status as we lived in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14102193 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7889384 HF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 No. Not that I can remember. No.
