\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7889384 HF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 From there, well I should imagine - just about the same distance, 'cos we lived in between the two schools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14102193 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 Did you have your midday meal at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7889384 HF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 Always came home, no meal - never - never had a meal at school, no.
