Well, we did like certain teachers better than others. Funnily enough I remember it now, that ever teacher had a kind - had a nickname, they were all nicknamed. And - some were regards as being very strict, one or two were regarded as b
eing very strict. And another man who was very well respected - never seemed to be strict but he kept discipline in his own - own queer way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14102193 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 Did any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11889103\charrsid815340 of them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
