, nor tidiness. The only thing - often, the thing that would happen in those days, very poor - children, you see 'em running about the streets with no shoes or stockings on, no boots or stockings on. If a - if a boy which I did see, a boy could go to - wo
uld go to school in his bare}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11889103\charrsid815340  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 feet the teacher'd send him home again.
