}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11889103\charrsid815340 writing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15428707\charrsid815340 , he said my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11889103\charrsid815340 writing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
